{"title":"Portfolio Weight Calculation for Multiple Stocks","markdown":{"headingText":"Portfolio Weight Calculation for Multiple Stocks","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n```{r}\n#| eval: true\n#| results: asis\n#| echo: false\n#| warning: false\nlibrary(webexercises)\n\n# Randomizing share prices\nprice_abt <- rnorm(1, mean = 60, sd = 8)\nprice_low <- rnorm(1, mean = 40, sd = 3)\nprice_bll <- rnorm(1, mean = 50, sd = 4)\n\n# Randomizing number of shares while ensuring total investment is consistent\ninvestment <- 20000\nshares_abt <- sample(100:300, 1)\nshares_low <- sample(100:300, 1)\nremaining_investment <- investment - (shares_abt * price_abt) - (shares_low * price_low)\nshares_bll <- round(remaining_investment / price_bll)\n\n# Compute values\nvalue_abt <- shares_abt * price_abt\nvalue_low <- shares_low * price_low\nvalue_bll <- shares_bll * price_bll\n\ntotal_value <- value_abt + value_low + value_bll\n\n# Ensure weights sum to 1\nweight_abt <- value_abt / total_value\nweight_low <- value_low / total_value\nweight_bll <- value_bll / total_value\n```\n\nSuppose you purchase **`r shares_abt`** shares of Company&nbsp;A at \\$**`r round(price_abt,2)`** per share, **`r shares_low`** shares of Company&nbsp;B at \\$**`r round(price_low,2)`** per share, and **`r shares_bll`** shares of Company&nbsp;C at \\$**`r round(price_bll,2)`** per share.\n\n::: {.question-block}\n\n<form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\" style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: row; gap: 6px;\">\n  <label for=\"module3_num_q2a\"><strong>1. What is the weight on Company&nbsp;A in your portfolio (in %)?</strong></label>\n  <input type=\"number\" id=\"module3_num_q2a\" name=\"module3_num_q2a\" placeholder=\"Enter value\" style=\"width: 150px;\"\n         data-correct-answer=`r round( weight_abt * 100 , 2 )` data-tolerance=\"0.01\" />\n</form>\n\n<div id=\"feedback-module3_num_q2a\" class=\"feedback\" data-status=\"\" style=\"display:none;\">\n✅ Weight on Company A = value_A / total_value × 100 = **`r round(weight_abt * 100, 2)`**%.\n</div>\n\n:::\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":""},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"knitr"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"notebook-links":true},"pandoc":{"standalone":true,"wrap":"none","default-image-extension":"png","to":"html","css":["../../../../include/webex.css"],"include-after-body":["../../../../include/webex.js"],"output-file":"module3_num_q2.html"},"language":{"toc-title-document":"Table of contents","toc-title-website":"On this page","related-formats-title":"Other Formats","related-notebooks-title":"Notebooks","source-notebooks-prefix":"Source","other-links-title":"Other Links","code-links-title":"Code Links","launch-dev-container-title":"Launch Dev Container","launch-binder-title":"Launch Binder","article-notebook-label":"Article Notebook","notebook-preview-download":"Down